FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AccessFailedCount", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName", g."Id" AS "Id0", g."AccessToken", g."AvatarUrl", g."HtmlUrl", g."Login", g."UserId"
    FROM "AspNetUsers" AS a
    LEFT JOIN "GithubUsers" AS g ON a."Id" = g."UserId"
    WHERE ((a."UserName" = @__authState_User_Identity_Name_0) AND ((a."UserName" IS NOT NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NOT NULL))) OR ((a."UserName" IS NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NULL))
    LIMIT 2
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."Id" = p."OwnerId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT i."Id", i."Message", i."ProjectId", i."UserId", p0."Id" AS "Id0", p0."Name", p0."OwnerId", r."Id" AS "Id1", r."Description", r."HtmlUrl", r."Name" AS "Name0", r."ProjectId" AS "ProjectId0", r."UserId" AS "UserId0"
    FROM "Invites" AS i
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p0 ON i."ProjectId" = p0."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r ON p0."Id" = r."ProjectId"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."UserId"
LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r0 ON t."Id" = r0."UserId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p1."ContributorId", p1."ProjectId", p2."Id", p2."Name", p2."OwnerId", r1."Id" AS "Id0", r1."Description", r1."HtmlUrl", r1."Name" AS "Name0", r1."ProjectId" AS "ProjectId0", r1."UserId"
    FROM "ProjectUsers" AS p1
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p2 ON p1."ProjectId" = p2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r1 ON p2."Id" = r1."ProjectId"
) AS t1 ON t."Id" = t1."ContributorId"
ORDER BY t."Id", p."Id", t0."Id", t0."Id0", r0."Id", t1."ContributorId", t1."ProjectId", t1."Id"

SELECT t."Id", t."AccessFailedCount", t."ConcurrencyStamp", t."Email", t."EmailConfirmed", t."LockoutEnabled", t."LockoutEnd", t."NormalizedEmail", t."NormalizedUserName", t."PasswordHash", t."PhoneNumber", t."PhoneNumberConfirmed", t."SecurityStamp", t."TwoFactorEnabled", t."UserName", t."Id0", t."AccessToken", t."AvatarUrl", t."HtmlUrl", t."Login", t."UserId", p."Id", p."Name", p."OwnerId", t0."ContributorId", t0."ProjectId", t0."Id", t0."Name", t0."OwnerId"
FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AccessFailedCount", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName", g."Id" AS "Id0", g."AccessToken", g."AvatarUrl", g."HtmlUrl", g."Login", g."UserId"
    FROM "AspNetUsers" AS a
    LEFT JOIN "GithubUsers" AS g ON a."Id" = g."UserId"
    WHERE ((a."UserName" = @__authState_User_Identity_Name_0) AND ((a."UserName" IS NOT NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NOT NULL))) OR ((a."UserName" IS NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NULL))
    LIMIT 2
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."Id" = p."OwnerId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."ContributorId", p0."ProjectId", p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."OwnerId"
    FROM "ProjectUsers" AS p0
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p1 ON p0."ProjectId" = p1."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ContributorId"
ORDER BY t."Id", p."Id", t0."ContributorId", t0."ProjectId", t0."Id"

FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AccessFailedCount", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName", g."Id" AS "Id0", g."AccessToken", g."AvatarUrl", g."HtmlUrl", g."Login", g."UserId"
    FROM "AspNetUsers" AS a
    LEFT JOIN "GithubUsers" AS g ON a."Id" = g."UserId"
    WHERE ((a."UserName" = @__authState_User_Identity_Name_0) AND ((a."UserName" IS NOT NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NOT NULL))) OR ((a."UserName" IS NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NULL))
    LIMIT 2
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."Id" = p."OwnerId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."ContributorId", p0."ProjectId", p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."OwnerId"
    FROM "ProjectUsers" AS p0
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p1 ON p0."ProjectId" = p1."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ContributorId"
ORDER BY t."Id", p."Id", t0."ContributorId", t0."ProjectId", t0."Id"

SELECT t."Id", t."AccessFailedCount", t."ConcurrencyStamp", t."Email", t."EmailConfirmed", t."LockoutEnabled", t."LockoutEnd", t."NormalizedEmail", t."NormalizedUserName", t."PasswordHash", t."PhoneNumber", t."PhoneNumberConfirmed", t."SecurityStamp", t."TwoFactorEnabled", t."UserName", t."Id0", t."AccessToken", t."AvatarUrl", t."HtmlUrl", t."Login", t."UserId", p."Id", p."Name", p."OwnerId", t0."ContributorId", t0."ProjectId", t0."Id", t0."Name", t0."OwnerId"
FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AccessFailedCount", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName", g."Id" AS "Id0", g."AccessToken", g."AvatarUrl", g."HtmlUrl", g."Login", g."UserId"
    FROM "AspNetUsers" AS a
    LEFT JOIN "GithubUsers" AS g ON a."Id" = g."UserId"
    WHERE ((a."UserName" = @__authState_User_Identity_Name_0) AND ((a."UserName" IS NOT NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NOT NULL))) OR ((a."UserName" IS NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NULL))
    LIMIT 2
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."Id" = p."OwnerId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."ContributorId", p0."ProjectId", p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."OwnerId"
    FROM "ProjectUsers" AS p0
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p1 ON p0."ProjectId" = p1."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ContributorId"
ORDER BY t."Id", p."Id", t0."ContributorId", t0."ProjectId", t0."Id"

    SELECT a."Id", a."AccessFailedCount", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName", g."Id" AS "Id0", g."AccessToken", g."AvatarUrl", g."HtmlUrl", g."Login", g."UserId"

    WHERE ((a."UserName" = @__authState_User_Identity_Name_0) AND ((a."UserName" IS NOT NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NOT NULL))) OR ((a."UserName" IS NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NULL))
    LIMIT 2
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."Id" = p."OwnerId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."ContributorId", p0."ProjectId", p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."OwnerId"
    FROM "ProjectUsers" AS p0
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p1 ON p0."ProjectId" = p1."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ContributorId"
ORDER BY t."Id", p."Id", t0."ContributorId", t0."ProjectId", t0."Id"

    SELECT a."Id", a."AccessFailedCount", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName", g."Id" AS "Id0", g."AccessToken", g."AvatarUrl", g."HtmlUrl", g."Login", g."UserId"

    LEFT JOIN "GithubUsers" AS g ON a."Id" = g."UserId"
    WHERE ((a."UserName" = @__authState_User_Identity_Name_0) AND ((a."UserName" IS NOT NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NOT NULL))) OR ((a."UserName" IS NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NULL))
    LIMIT 2
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."Id" = p."OwnerId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."ContributorId", p0."ProjectId", p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."OwnerId"
    FROM "ProjectUsers" AS p0
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p1 ON p0."ProjectId" = p1."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ContributorId"

FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AccessFailedCount", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName", g."Id" AS "Id0", g."AccessToken", g."AvatarUrl", g."HtmlUrl", g."Login", g."UserId"

    LEFT JOIN "GithubUsers" AS g ON a."Id" = g."UserId"
    WHERE ((a."UserName" = @__authState_User_Identity_Name_0) AND ((a."UserName" IS NOT NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NOT NULL))) OR ((a."UserName" IS NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NULL))
    LIMIT 2
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."Id" = p."OwnerId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."ContributorId", p0."ProjectId", p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."OwnerId"
    FROM "ProjectUsers" AS p0
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p1 ON p0."ProjectId" = p1."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ContributorId"
ORDER BY t."Id", p."Id", t0."ContributorId", t0."ProjectId", t0."Id"

FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AccessFailedCount", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName", g."Id" AS "Id0", g."AccessToken", g."AvatarUrl", g."HtmlUrl", g."Login", g."UserId"
    FROM "AspNetUsers" AS a
    LEFT JOIN "GithubUsers" AS g ON a."Id" = g."UserId"
    WHERE ((a."UserName" = @__authState_User_Identity_Name_0) AND ((a."UserName" IS NOT NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NOT NULL))) OR ((a."UserName" IS NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NULL))
    LIMIT 2
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."Id" = p."OwnerId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."ContributorId", p0."ProjectId", p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."OwnerId"
    FROM "ProjectUsers" AS p0
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p1 ON p0."ProjectId" = p1."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ContributorId"
ORDER BY t."Id", p."Id", t0."ContributorId", t0."ProjectId", t0."Id"

    SELECT p1."ContributorId", p1."ProjectId", p2."Id", p2."Name", p2."OwnerId", r1."Id" AS "Id0", r1."Description", r1."HtmlUrl", r1."Name" AS "Name0", r1."ProjectId" AS "ProjectId0", r1."UserId"
    FROM "ProjectUsers" AS p1
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p2 ON p1."ProjectId" = p2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r1 ON p2."Id" = r1."ProjectId"
) AS t1 ON t."Id" = t1."ContributorId"
ORDER BY t."Id", p."Id", t0."Id", t0."Id0", r0."Id", t1."ContributorId", t1."ProjectId", t1."Id"

    SELECT a."Id", a."AccessFailedCount", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName", g."Id" AS "Id0", g."AccessToken", g."AvatarUrl", g."HtmlUrl", g."Login", g."UserId"

    WHERE ((a."UserName" = @__authState_User_Identity_Name_0) AND ((a."UserName" IS NOT NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NOT NULL))) OR ((a."UserName" IS NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NULL))

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT i."Id", i."Message", i."ProjectId", i."Status", i."UserId", p0."Id" AS "Id0", p0."Name", p0."OwnerId", r."Id" AS "Id1", r."Description", r."HtmlUrl", r."Name" AS "Name0", r."ProjectId" AS "ProjectId0", r."UserId" AS "UserId0"

    LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r ON p0."Id" = r."ProjectId"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."UserId"

) AS t1 ON t."Id" = t1."ContributorId"

FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AccessFailedCount", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName", g."Id" AS "Id0", g."AccessToken", g."AvatarUrl", g."HtmlUrl", g."Login", g."UserId"

    LEFT JOIN "GithubUsers" AS g ON a."Id" = g."UserId"
    WHERE ((a."UserName" = @__authState_User_Identity_Name_0) AND ((a."UserName" IS NOT NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NOT NULL))) OR ((a."UserName" IS NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NULL))
    LIMIT 2
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."Id" = p."OwnerId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT i."Id", i."Message", i."ProjectId", i."Status", i."UserId", p0."Id" AS "Id0", p0."Name", p0."OwnerId", r."Id" AS "Id1", r."Description", r."HtmlUrl", r."Name" AS "Name0", r."ProjectId" AS "ProjectId0", r."UserId" AS "UserId0"
    FROM "Invites" AS i
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p0 ON i."ProjectId" = p0."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r ON p0."Id" = r."ProjectId"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."UserId"
LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r0 ON t."Id" = r0."UserId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p1."ContributorId", p1."ProjectId", p2."Id", p2."Name", p2."OwnerId", r1."Id" AS "Id0", r1."Description", r1."HtmlUrl", r1."Name" AS "Name0", r1."ProjectId" AS "ProjectId0", r1."UserId"
    FROM "ProjectUsers" AS p1
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p2 ON p1."ProjectId" = p2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r1 ON p2."Id" = r1."ProjectId"
) AS t1 ON t."Id" = t1."ContributorId"
ORDER BY t."Id", p."Id", t0."Id", t0."Id0", r0."Id", t1."ContributorId", t1."ProjectId", t1."Id"

    SELECT a."Id", a."AccessFailedCount", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName", g."Id" AS "Id0", g."AccessToken", g."AvatarUrl", g."HtmlUrl", g."Login", g."UserId"

    WHERE ((a."UserName" = @__authState_User_Identity_Name_0) AND ((a."UserName" IS NOT NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NOT NULL))) OR ((a."UserName" IS NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NULL))

) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."Id" = p."OwnerId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT i."Id", i."Message", i."ProjectId", i."Status", i."UserId", p0."Id" AS "Id0", p0."Name", p0."OwnerId", r."Id" AS "Id1", r."Description", r."HtmlUrl", r."Name" AS "Name0", r."ProjectId" AS "ProjectId0", r."UserId" AS "UserId0"

    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p0 ON i."ProjectId" = p0."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r ON p0."Id" = r."ProjectId"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."UserId"
LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r0 ON t."Id" = r0."UserId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p1."ContributorId", p1."ProjectId", p2."Id", p2."Name", p2."OwnerId", r1."Id" AS "Id0", r1."Description", r1."HtmlUrl", r1."Name" AS "Name0", r1."ProjectId" AS "ProjectId0", r1."UserId"

    FROM "Invites" AS i
